 0567: 	"""
 0568: 	Given an alleletable file, this function will split the alleletable into independent
 0569: 	lineage groups and estimate the indel formation probabilities. This is done by
 0570: 	treating each intBC as an independent observation and counting how many intBC contain
 0571: 	a specific mutation, irrespective of the cell.
 0572: 
 0573: 	:param at:
 0574: 		The allele table pandas DataFrame
 0575: 	:param group_var:
 0576: 		Columns by which to group and count indels. This will effectively serve as the denominator when calculating the 
 0577: 		frequenceis (i.e. N intBCs or M * N_m for M lineage groups and N_m intBCs per lineage groups if you group by intBC and LG)
 0578: 	:return:
 0579: 		An M x 2 pandas DataFrame mapping all M mutations to the frequency and raw counts
 0580: 		of how many intBC this mutation appeared on.
